<i>♪ Nothing came out ♪</i>

456
00:28:50,688 --> 00:28:54,107
<i>♪ when I opened my mouth to you ♪</i>

457
00:28:54,108 --> 00:28:57,777
<i>♪ Do you feel me?
'Cause I'm feeling myself ♪</i>

458
00:28:57,778 --> 00:28:59,779
<i>♪ Why don't you feel me? ♪</i>

459
